{% block subject %}
    {% spaceless %}
        Specialty School Application Teacher Recommendation Form
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}

{{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }} has applied to the {{school_name}}.  This application requires a Recommendation be completed by their teacher.

Please visit the link below and complete the Teacher Recommendation for this student.
{{ recommendation_url }}

We have been notified of technical difficulties and therefore, have extended the completion deadline to Friday, February 16, 2018.  Please contact the Attendance Office should you have any questions or concerns.

This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies.  {{ 'magnet.contact'|trans|raw }}

Thanks,
Specialty School Program
{% endblock body_text %}

